评论概述: Poor quality and very small.Total waste of money

评论详情: I’m all for an inexpensive handbag but this one was made with extremely cheap material. The dividers inside the bag were much like paper and noisy to touch. The color was supposed to be brown and Black but look more like maroon and brown. It has zippers on each side that lead to nowhere. I didn’t pay much for the bag but I definitely expected more than this.
